{"tid":687531,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（文長）我只係臭雞一名","createTime":"2018-06-02T10:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T16:14:55.000Z","uid":86148,"like":1,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e075f263c011a41d77b9eb5e5e131811b872eac9","tid":687531,"uid":86148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:54:05.000Z","msg":"曾經我有一個對我好好嘅男朋友，<br />\n好照顧我，好錫我，所有野都就哂我，為我付出好多好多，<br />\n我敢講冇任何一個男仔可以比得上佢。<br />\n<br />\n或者人就係咁唔知足，<br />\n我一開始冇為呢段關係認真，<br />\n背住佢出去搵其他男仔發生關係，<br />\n成日上網識人撩人，<br />\n事後仲要若無其事咁對住佢。<br />\n<br />\n到後來，我慢慢開始發現佢嘅好，<br />\n我開始珍惜呢段關係，<br />\n我學做一個乖嘅女朋友，<br />\n冇再搵其他男仔，好努力咁去維繫呢段感情，<br />\n呢段時間我地真係好開心好幸福，<br />\n每日見到佢就已經夠，<br />\n我以為可以同佢一直行落去。<br />\n<br />\n但係有啲人就係死性不改，<br />\n之後我不段用藉口去見其中一個sp，<br />\n仲要講到我同呢個sp只係普通朋友，<br />\n東窗事發之後，我仲要同人地講係我男朋友小氣，<br />\n我冇幫住我男朋友，反而幫住一個sp講說話。<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢到，可能你會覺得我好賤，<br />\n係，我的確好賤，<br />\n我唔明白點解自己要做出啲咁過份嘅事去傷害一個咁錫我嘅人，<br />\n我唔明白自己到底喺到做緊啲乜野，<br />\n我好後悔，好內疚，我好憎我自己，<br />\n如果一開頭我可以重視佢多啲，<br />\n如果我冇做啲咁過份嘅野，<br />\n我地真係可以一直好開心好幸福咁行落去。<br />\n<br />\n我估樓下有好多人會鬧我係臭雞，<br />\n唔知道你睇唔睇到呢個post，<br />\n如果你睇到嘅話，<br />\n希望你知道，我唔值得你再為我流淚，<br />\n你一定會遇到個好好嘅女仔，<br />\n唔需要覺得可惜，<br />\n你望下啲人點鬧我，<br />\n你就會知道其實冇野值得你喊，<br />\n對唔住，我整到你個心好痛，<br />\n我好想去改好，我好想去彌補，<br />\n但係已經冇用，<br />\n唔知幾時開始你見到我就只會喊，<br />\n冇咗我或者係件好事。<br />\n<br />\n「我最大的遺憾，是你的遺憾與我有關。」<br />\n肥寶，祝你幸福，<br />\n當發咗一場惡夢，<br />\n夢醒就要忘記，<br />\n多謝你。"},{"pid":"b2ea7d93675211f12b75ba48c04bcec1cd9093f4","tid":687531,"uid":65743,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/185459_39c4ca3383191d9f28e2711774e5c768.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F185459_39c4ca3383191d9f28e2711774e5c768.gif&h=a02d6700&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8057275a9c019f99112cd17d6e4d3ac29095c912","tid":687531,"uid":76913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:55:50.000Z","msg":"I know"},{"pid":"cf366d52757d355d71ca63250595f146b898c0da","tid":687531,"uid":24675,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:58:19.000Z","msg":"當e 到係Facebook?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948ca2fdb74471b7f4694b8768caafa86f33b976","tid":687531,"uid":67655,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:58:41.000Z","msg":"又作文<br />\n男人做咩雞呀<br />\n你係咪痴撚咗線呀"},{"pid":"09ab34dbdd67a9ec2efb8698b8ff76c8f136e860","tid":687531,"uid":86148,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"cf366d52757d355d71ca63250595f146b898c0da","tid":687531,"uid":24675,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:58:19.000Z","msg":"當e 到係Facebook?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:01:23.000Z","msg":"對唔住，我知道佢有上連登，<br />\n我只係想佢見到，<br />\n煩到你唔好意思。"},{"pid":"adb3c374a48d5ac61962c31e63cbcc0107b5a39d","tid":687531,"uid":102299,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:56:38.000Z","msg":"如果你前度見到呢個po嘅話，恭喜你呀同隻臭雞散咗"},{"pid":"42473b03027f83bfec77c6deaf73032864807afe","tid":687531,"uid":113007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:58:57.000Z","msg":"0分重作"},{"pid":"c23fe0c12c9e4a875ca996ec06d88614fea0f128","tid":687531,"uid":61954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/12/201603_48c20e2a611dddef8a1cc92c7901fe33.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F12%2F201603_48c20e2a611dddef8a1cc92c7901fe33.gif&h=19bd7a45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64941b85648c9f8ecf4dceb51b78453506fe0e84","tid":687531,"uid":123956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小姐你給帽男朋友便算吧啦"},{"pid":"28b0f121179b44103b3d68f66fe9b0a562731973","tid":687531,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T12:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話你臭雞都侮辱左雞啦<br />\n港女係咁上下賤ga la<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d440e17a79838b2dfd1b9d4bce4ba0aa37d88c","tid":687531,"uid":16901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"屌你 垃撚垃 搵佢講番聲對唔住都要啦"},{"pid":"62d943c524bd62d99214c9182e6d69adf641da3c","tid":687531,"uid":145490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/231621_85487a23da5b876d8e126b5162cfc122.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F231621_85487a23da5b876d8e126b5162cfc122.png&h=189d5516&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2efa704d2e03cc89c38d53822d3701c58720a9b5","tid":687531,"uid":173918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:36:48.000Z","msg":"你唔再係為自己而活<br />\n唔好浪費我既出現<br />\n記住最後一晚我同你講既所有野"},{"pid":"994628a8202a36a94fe926d8cd5318ab351e30b8","tid":687531,"uid":2407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:49:57.000Z","msg":"你漏左 #mk"},{"pid":"41c55b990f3748f92827be6cacc78aacf24528ee","tid":687531,"uid":3688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:53:12.000Z","msg":"真係唔好問點解香港冇好男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd2c0517402c3445f58ce6c565d7e81bde04790","tid":687531,"uid":63768,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T18:11:43.000Z","msg":"臭雞，係度打篇文諗住贖罪<br />\n香港有幾多人就係因為你呢啲臭雞變晒厹<br />\n其實你咁樣係度打有咩用<br />\n錯又唔敢認<br />\n到呢一刻，你都只不過係柒左又要攞光環嘅臭雞<br />\n唔撚識愛人唔好衝出黎柒啦"},{"pid":"140341f15de0e745758a17ff1ba682c14136b6eb","tid":687531,"uid":94007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T18:12:12.000Z","msg":"肥寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed1d45e941ece0fe9bd1105a31e8e25373dc675","tid":687531,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T18:14:49.000Z","msg":"做好男人既下場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f8010ac2001a4b761d2e1da9e19e905e942bd2","tid":687531,"uid":159659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"140341f15de0e745758a17ff1ba682c14136b6eb","tid":687531,"uid":94007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T18:12:12.000Z","msg":"肥寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T18:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d335952aea0c59161b6521fb75c3a27e050df188","tid":687531,"uid":183997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T18:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b95f61ee65edf386a55bf7b44df7bdbb1707110","tid":687531,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T18:26:11.000Z","msg":